title: Do the work
text: Everybody loves the idea of making a bunch of money trading options, but not too many people put in the requisite work to make it happen. Right now it's 18 30 Pacific time. I am just getting started on more analysis and I've been doing this for 16 years. It doesn't stop. The outcome is really, really cool. You unlock your freedom. But if you think that you're going to get there by not doing the work, you're just setting yourself up for failure. Be an outlight or see a little later.
